translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,36,"Ngabo bamphulaphulayo uMthunywa kuphela, abaza kuba nohoyo, kodwa ke ngokuphathelene nabafileyo (abahedeni) uAllâh Uza kubanyusela kuYe, yaye kukuYe apho baza kubuyela khona"
  6,37,"Kananjalo bathi: “Kutheni kungekho mqondiso uthunyelwayo kuye ovela eNkosini yakhe?” Yithi wena: “Inene uAllâh Uyakwazi ukuthumela imiqondiso kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi nto.”"
  6,38,"Akukho sidalwa sinyakazayo emhlabeni, kungekho nantaka ibhabhayo ngeempiko zayo, koko zingamabandla njengani. Akukho nto Siyishiyeleleyo eNcwadini, kwaye (zonke) ziza kubuyela eNkosini azo"
  6,39,"Abo bangazamkeliyo iiVesi zeThu, bazizithulu nezimumu ezisebumnyameni. UAllâh Ulahlekisa lowo Athande (ukumlahlekisa) Aze Akhokelele eNdleleni ethe Tye lowo Athande (ukumkhokelela)"
  6,40,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Khanindixeleleni, ukuba isohlwayo sika-Allâh singehla phezu kwenu, kungenjalo iYure ifike kuni, ingaba beningabiza komnye ngaphandle koAllâh? (phendulani) ukuba ninenyaniso"
  6,41,"Nakanye, beniya kubiza kuYe Yedwa, yaye ukuba Ebethanda Ebeza kuyisusa inkxalabo kuni leyo beniya kuMbiza ngenxa yayo nize futhi nililibale ngelo xesha naliphi na ihlulelane enilayamanisa naYe.”"
  6,42,"Inene, Sathumela (abaThunywa) kwizizwe ezininzi phambi kwakho kananjalo Sazithwaxa ngentlupheko enkulu nangelahleko yempilo khon’ukuze zizinikele (ngentobeko)"
  6,43,"Ngethuba lokufika kwesohlwayo seThu kuzo, kwakutheni zingazithobi? Ukusuka apho iintliziyo zazo zasuka zaqaqadeka noShaytân wenza kwabonakala kulungile kuzo oko (kugwenxa) zazikwenza"
  6,44,"Ke kaloku zathi zisakusilibala (isilumkiso) eso zazikhunjuzwe ngaso, Sazivulela amasango abo bonke (ubuncwane) bezinto, kwala xa ziphakathi naphakathi kolo lonwabo zazilunikiwe, Sasuka ngesaquphe Sazithabatha (ngesohlwayo) Yeha kuzo! Zagaxeleka entshabalalweni zinokuzisola okunzulu nosizi"